Slovakia Will Vote on Euro Fund Overhaul by Oct. 14, Miklos Says

-- B y   M a r k   D e e n
-- 
2011-10-03T22:28:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-03/slovakia-will-vote-on-euro-fund-overhaul-by-oct-14-miklos-says.html
Slovakia ’s parliament will probably
vote on a euro-area agreement to overhaul the region’s bailout
fund by Oct. 11 and will vote by Oct. 14 at the latest, Finance
Minister Ivan Miklos said.  Miklos also said he won’t recommend that Slovakia seek
collateral for loans to  Greece . He spoke to reporters in
Luxembourg.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mark Deen in Luxembourg at 
 markdeen@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jeff Black at 
 jblack25@bloomberg.net  